c: 17
v: 97
t: "wmn yhdh allah fahu almuhtadi 'iilaa alhq, wamin yudlilh fykhdhlh wyakilh 'iilaa nafsih fala hadi lah min dun allh, whwla' alddulal yabeathuhum allah yawm alqyamt, wyhshrhm ealaa wjwhhm, wahum la yarawn wala yantiqun wala ysmewn, masirihim 'iilaa nar jahanam almlthbt, kulama sakan lhybha, wkhmdt narha, zidnahum narana multahibatan mtajjt"